## Candidate requirements

Each candidate must describe:
- candidate ID, using the session namespace pattern {{.SubjectID}}.cand.NNN in reasoning even though the backend assigns persisted IDs
- repository/session scope
- source paths
- functionality description
- why it is reusable
- project-specific coupling
- suggested module kind
- target language
- dependencies
- risks
- tests found
- missing tests
- extraction notes
- proposed typed ports
- proposed workbench node shape

Focus especially on:
- OpenTelemetry metrics
- traces and logs
- agent lifecycle events
- agent administration
- orchestration
- process supervision
- workspace management
- repository checkout
- task queues
- model/provider abstraction
- deployment helpers
- webhooks
- audit logs
- admin APIs

